1. Final project of CIS555

YASE is a mini search engine which has an index size of about one million web pages. It is designed to get relevant search results within a reasonable limit of time. It consists of four major components: Crawler, Indexer, PageRank and Search Engine. By the way, YASE stands for Yet Another Search Engine. Details are in Final Report.

2. Features Implemented:

Distributed Crawler
Distributed Indexer
Search Interface
PageRank calculator
IDF caculator

